# (GAME 1) ~ MeinHistoryRPG

Simple RPG project made for fun and learning.

No frameworks.
No AI generated code.
Just programming like the old internet days.

## About

MeinHistoryRPG is an experimental RPG game project focused on gameplay ideas, classic mechanics and old-school development style.

This repository is part of my personal game experiments collection.

The project is being built manually step by step without depending on automated generators or modern bloated toolchains.

## Features

* RPG mechanics
* Experimental systems
* Retro development philosophy
* Pure code editing
* Personal learning project

## Project Status

Work in progress.

Things may change, break or be rewritten completely.

## Philosophy

This project is made like the old days:

* writing code manually
* learning by trial and error
* no copy paste from AI
* no overengineering
* no unnecessary dependencies

Just code, ideas and experimentation.

## Goals

* Learn game development
* Improve programming skills
* Experiment with RPG systems
* Keep the spirit of old independent development alive

